                        <p class="">These Terms and Conditions constitute a binding contract between BUYER and SELLER (as defined in the Purchase Order) and are referred to herein as either “Terms and Conditions” or this “Agreement”. BUYER accepts these Terms and Conditions by placing an order with SELLER through a Purchase Order.</p>
