                        <p class=""><strong>3) Cancellation/Return Policy:&nbsp;</strong><em>IN NO EVENT WILL RETURNS BE ALLOWED FOR ANY EQUIPMENT SOLD TO BUYER. BUYER ACKNOWLEDGES UPON EXECUTION OF THE PURCHASE ORDER SELLER PURCHASES ANY EQUIPMENT FROM THIRD PARTIES AND SUCH EQUIPMENT IS REGISTERED IN BUYER’S NAME AND THEREFORE NON-REFUNDABLE.</em></p>
